{quote}
{color:#d04437}Zhankun->{color} Yeah, It's a legacy in WIP patch. Will remove that. One thing to clarify is that the DevicePluginAdapter itsefl is actually a ResourcePlugin. It is added into ResourcePluginManager's pluginMap.

